data.title: Horrible
data.text: Food was horrible. Ordered it to go. Got there early and should of checked it because it was cold in the 5 block drive home.  Portions were ridiculously small and not cooked properly. First time and last time at a Webb.  I'd rather support local diners that take some pride in their food.

data.title: Car show lunch stop
data.text:
Considering there was a huge car show going on in the main street in front, they really took our order fast and got served in timely fashion.
 It was clean in there. For being a George Webb I think the food was pretty good.
